headline: A Look at UPS’s Valuation After Recent Share Price Declines
summary: It is hard to ignore when United Parcel Service (UPS) stock takes a dip, as it did recently. With shares sliding over the month and even more sharply across the year, investors are starting to wonder whether the delivery giant is simply out of favor, or if there is a deeper story behind the persistent drop. In a market that often sends mixed signals, understanding what is really in play for UPS is more important than ever. So far this year, UPS shares have fallen more than 32%, including a...
